{"tid":2356971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧︰考慮制裁拘捕香港民主派相關人士","createTime":"2021-01-07T06:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:33:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":135,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"32640c218c713dbc5b5bc1aaca56aacf9e54be05","tid":2356971,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧發聲明，關注香港53名組織和參與民主派初選人士被捕，考慮對相關人士實施制裁。蓬佩奧形容事件令人憤慨，亦再次提醒中國共產黨對人民和法治的蔑視，認為被捕的人士只是實踐民主權利，並無干犯任何罪行，促請當局立即無條件釋放他們。 <br />\n<br />\n他又指香港人民受到中共壓迫，美國支持香港人民，不會袖手旁觀，會考慮對任何相關的人士和實體實施制裁或其他限制，包括對香港駐美國的經濟貿易辦事處施加限制，以及對削弱香港民主的官員採取即時的行動。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又表示，被捕人士中包括一名美國公民，強調不會容忍對美國公民的任意拘留或騷擾行動。 蓬佩奧又在聲明中宣布，美國駐聯合國大使克拉夫特將會訪問台灣，形容台灣是一個可靠的伙伴，民主政治充滿活力。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373792&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5sF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=b94fb919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373792</a>"},{"pid":"ad9b9b25db6a1fee68fd564d1ae0a2179cf0e9d0","tid":2356971,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642005cec841b67d7a875f0b367869ec9f322183","tid":2356971,"uid":24730,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"希望制裁全港黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45b5773d071859292422095a3d53efb41eaf6c9","tid":2356971,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a